    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/User_Interface\" title=\"User Interface\">User Interface</a> * <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> * Banksia GUI</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:130px;\"><a href=\"https://banksiagui.com/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/d/d0/Bsicon.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Bsicon.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>BanksiaGUI logo</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Banksia GUI</b>,<br />\na free <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">chess GUI</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> and <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compliant, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cross-platform\">cross platform</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, written by <a href=\"/Pham_Hong_Nguyen\" title=\"Pham Hong Nguyen\">Nguyen Pham</a>, first published in 2019 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nBanksiaGUI binaries are available from the <i>BanksiaGUI site</i>.\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Chess_Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Variants</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Screenshot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Screenshot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Variants\">Chess Variants</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia_GUI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Variants\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> Standard chess</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a> or Fischer Random Chess (FRC)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Screenshot\">Screenshot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia_GUI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Screenshot\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"https://banksiagui.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Bsgscreen01.jpg\" src=\"/images/8/8f/Bsgscreen01.jpg\" width=\"520\" height=\"484\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p>BanksiaGUI <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia_GUI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>A brief summary\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chess_Game\" title=\"Chess Game\">Playing</a> and analyzing chess games</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tournament_Manager\" title=\"Tournament Manager\">Tournament Manager</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">Database</a> view and create</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Book</a> view and create</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a> - <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">book</a> format</li>\n<li> High Configurable Interface</li>\n<li> Detailed information thinking process</li>\n<li> Support statics table of <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero#Lc0\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Lc0</a></li>\n<li> Support WDL statics</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Engine_Benchmark&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Engine Benchmark (page does not exist)\">Engine Benchmark</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a> (Fischer Random Chess)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Lichess_Bots&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Lichess Bots (page does not exist)\">Lichess Bots</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chess_Server\" title=\"Chess Server\">Internet Chess Server</a></li>\n<li> Network connect and play</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Algebraic_Chess_Notation\" title=\"Algebraic Chess Notation\">Algebraic Chess Notation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Extended_Position_Description\" title=\"Extended Position Description\">Extended Position Description</a> (EPD)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Forsyth-Edwards_Notation\" title=\"Forsyth-Edwards Notation\">Forsyth-Edwards Notation</a> (FEN)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">Portable Game Notation</a> (PGN)</li>\n<li> Support of 3 languages for the GUI</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> protocol</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> protocol 2</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clipboard_%28software%29\">Clipboard</a> for Games and Positions</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mac_OS\" title=\"Mac OS\">Mac OS</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia_GUI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Banksia\" title=\"Banksia\">Banksia</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ChessGUI\" title=\"ChessGUI\">ChessGUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia_GUI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71157&amp;hilit=banksia\">Banksia - Yet another Chess Tournament Manager</a> by <a href=\"/Pham_Hong_Nguyen\" title=\"Pham Hong Nguyen\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 01, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72350\">Banksia GUI released</a> by <a href=\"/Pham_Hong_Nguyen\" title=\"Pham Hong Nguyen\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76948\">leela</a> by <a href=\"/Stuart_Cracraft\" title=\"Stuart Cracraft\">Stuart Cracraft</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 29, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=IPhone&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"IPhone (page does not exist)\">iPhone</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia_GUI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://banksiagui.com/\">Banksia GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/nguyenpham/banksia\">GitHub - Banksia - a Chess tournament manager</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Banksia\" title=\"Banksia\">Banksia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwzPwT0syFRiNILDpf6Q0KQ\">Banksia GUI tutorial</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Videos</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/RwLwscKXyO8?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd>\n<dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/TIn5kM3Eta0?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia_GUI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://BanksiaGUI.com:\">A portable, simple, desktop workbench for chess players and analysts</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72350\">Banksia GUI released</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://banksiagui.com/\">Banksia GUI</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301060439\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 83/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 210/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 52/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7334-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301060439 and revision id 25932\n -->\n"
